        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The passenger is stationary relative to the shore because the boat is moving at <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"5 meters per second\"><math alttext=\"5 meters per second\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>5</mn><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mtext>m/s</mtext></math></span></span> relative to the shore and the passenger is moving at <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"5 meters per second\"><math alttext=\"5 meters per second\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>5</mn><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mtext>m/s</mtext></math></span></span> relative to the boat in the opposite direction.</p>",
        "value": "i3"
      },
      {
